    {
      "title": "Algorithm 1: ISW tiled multiplication\nInput: Independent shares of a and b\nOutput: Shares c_i of ab\nfor i \\leftarrow 1 to d + 1 do\nfor j \\neq i do\na_i:T_{i,j} \\leftarrow a_i:T_i;\nb_j: T_{i,j} \\leftarrow b_j: T_j;\nend\nend\nfor i \\leftarrow 1 to d + 1 do\nfor j \\leftarrow i + 1 to d + 1 do\n(u_{i,j} \\leftarrow a_i b_j + r_{i,j}) : T_{i,j};\n(u_{j,i} \\leftarrow a_j b_i + r_{i,j}) : T_{j,i};\nu_{i,j}: T_i \\leftarrow u_{i,j}: T_{i,j};\nu_{j,i}:T_j \\leftarrow u_{j,i}:T_{j,i};\nend\nend\nfor i \\leftarrow 1 to d + 1 do\n(c_i \\leftarrow a_i b_i + \\sum_{j \\neq i} u_{i,j}) : T_i;\nend",
